snippet.title: Foxtale Demo - Play Now for Free!
snippet.description:
Download the free demo now and lay waste to a valley of robots! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3215570/Foxtale/

The awesome trailer music is "Space Cowboy" by Voltz Supreme! Check out his Bandcamp...
https://voltzsupreme.bandcamp.com/album/galactic-cowboys

In Foxtale, play as a little fox and save your planet from an intergalactic space invasion! The demo releases February 12th. Wishlist now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3215570/Foxtale/
